    %% Flows
    Client -->|"HTTPS+gRPC/2746<br/>TLS<br/>Bearer Token / SSO JWT"| ArgoServer
    ArgoServer -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Delegated SA Token"| K8sAPI
    ArgoServer -->|"TCP/5432<br/>TLS (config)<br/>Username/Password"| DB
    ArgoServer -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuth2"| OIDC

    WFController -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token<br/>Watch CRDs, Create Pods"| K8sAPI

    WFPod -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token<br/>Status Updates"| K8sAPI
    WFPod -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Cloud Credentials<br/>Artifact Upload"| S3

    Prometheus -->|"HTTP/9090<br/>plaintext<br/>No Auth"| WFController
    Prometheus -->|"HTTPS/2746<br/>TLS<br/>Bearer Token"| ArgoServer

